<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[سورة العصر]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قال الله عزَّ وجلَّ:</span> <span class="c2">(وَالْعَصْرِ (١)</span> إِنَّ الْإِنْسَانَ لَفِي خُسْرٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> إِلَّا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَعَمِلُوا الصَّالِحَاتِ وَتَوَاصَوْا بِالْحَقِّ وَتَوَاصَوْا بِالصَّبْرِ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">المجموع:</span> المقدمة:<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قال الشَّافِعِي رحمه الله:</span> لو ما أنزل الله حجة على خلقه إلا هذه السورة<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>لكفتهم.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قال الشَّافِعِي رحمه اللَّه:</span> الناس في غفلة عن هذه السورة: <span class="c2">(وَاَلعَصر. .)</span> .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>